      <section id="details">
        <h2 class="gem-c-heading gem-c-heading--font-size-27 gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Details</h2>


        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>Paper by <abbr title="Scientific Pandemic Influenza Group on Modelling, Operational sub-group">SPI-M-O</abbr> on local interventions and spatial scales. It was considered at <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/sage-meetings-august-2020#meeting-50,-6-august-2020" class="govuk-link"><abbr title="Scientific Advisory Group for Emergencies">SAGE</abbr> 50</a> on 6 August 2020.</p>

<p>The paper is the assessment of the evidence at the time of writing. As new evidence or data emerges, <abbr title="Scientific Advisory Group for Emergencies">SAGE</abbr> updates its advice accordingly.</p>

<p>This paper should be read alongside:</p>

<ul>
  <li>
<a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/spi-b-areas-of-intervention-local-lockdown-measures-to-control-outbreaks-of-covid-19-during-the-national-release-phase-30-july-2020" class="govuk-link"><abbr title="Independent Scientific Pandemic Influenza Group on Behaviours">SPI-B</abbr>: Areas of intervention (‘local lockdown’) measures to control outbreaks of <abbr title="coronavirus">COVID-19</abbr> during the national release phase, 30 July 2020</a>, tabled at <abbr title="Scientific Advisory Group for Emergencies">SAGE</abbr> 49</li>
  <li>
<a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/spi-m-o-consensus-statement-on-covid-19-5-august-2020" class="govuk-link"><abbr title="Scientific Pandemic Influenza Group on Modelling, Operational sub-group">SPI-M-O</abbr>: Consensus statement on <abbr title="coronavirus">COVID-19</abbr>, 5 August 2020</a>, as tabled at <abbr title="Scientific Advisory Group for Emergencies">SAGE</abbr> 50</li>
</ul>

<p>These documents are released as pre-print publications that have provided the government with rapid evidence during an emergency. These documents have not been peer-reviewed and there is no restriction on authors submitting and publishing this evidence in peer-reviewed journals.</p>

<p>Redactions in this document have been made to remove any security markings.</p>

</div>
</div>

      </section>
    </div>

